Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.59,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,{\r原文字幕}[Squawking]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:13.39,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,{\r原文字幕}[Creatures speaking alien languages]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.39,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,吉姆！  噢！  吉姆！等等我！\N{\r原文字幕}[DOPPLER] Jim! Oh, Jim! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.68,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,{\r原文字幕}[Clanking]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.51,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,{\r原文字幕}[Breathing deeply]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.48,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,呃  吉姆  我们应该趁这个机会\N{\r原文字幕}Well, Jim, this should be a wonderful opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.82,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,好好相互了解一下\N{\r原文字幕}for the two of us to get to know one another.
